href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=HkyGcFaseOEI6%2F2OHYoWK4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=9b2d8617\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"1b38fa55f1f1e51edfaccda442b366fe09691ef9","tid":887491,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"176abf85dddadeb2591d5c42eacb52965de08a19","tid":887491,"uid":187108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"48cc426372696a071f858c9f7e9205affcfe69e1","tid":887491,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e82d0874f53369ac78c5c996ef88d41c7aec878a","tid":887491,"uid":187108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:16:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:17:06.000Z","msg":"？？？？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T03:17:58.000Z","msg":"我日日都咁覺得，好想追尋屬於我嘅人生意義"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T04:50:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}